TransientWindow.label:
Standard LibreOffice Save As file dialog.
Title: "Save As" / "Uložit jako" / "Speichern unter" (locale-dependent).
Detection: SALSUBFRAME process=soffice.bin, title contains "Save" or locale equivalent.
Interaction via KeyWin.exe:
  Type a path:  SENDKEYS "C:\path\to\file.odt"  then SENDKEYS {ENTER}
  Cancel:       SENDKEYS {ESC}
